        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A three-minute energy statement practice from Day 25 of the MONEY program. The statement works with readiness: not whether you have the deposit yet, but whether you have removed the internal veto on the possibility. Say it as a plain declarative.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to energy statements? Read ",
